---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Lavelle Pty Ltd is an Australian company owned and directed by Sky Lavelle, providing senior project management consulting, PMO resource development and digital asset activities."
>
  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Lavelle Pty Ltd</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          An Australian company providing senior project delivery consulting, PMO resources and digital asset development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT CONTENT -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Lavelle Pty Ltd is an Australian company owned and directed by Sky Lavelle.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Sky is both a director and employee of the company, providing senior project management and consulting services through Lavelle Pty Ltd while also leading the company's PMO resource development and digital asset activities.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          The company's work is grounded in practical delivery experience, commercial discipline and a focus on building useful systems that can scale over time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW WE OPERATE -->
  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Operating model</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">How We Operate</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Lavelle Pty Ltd combines hands-on delivery experience with digital asset development. Consulting work provides real-world delivery insight, while the digital asset portfolio and PMO resources turn that knowledge into reusable systems, content, tools and commercial products.
        </p>
        <p>
          This operating model allows the company to serve clients directly while also building long-term owned assets.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT THE COMPANY DOES -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Company activities</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">What Lavelle Pty Ltd Does</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Senior Consulting</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Senior project management and consulting services through Sky Lavelle for complex technology, digital transformation, procurement, governance and business change engagements.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/consulting"
            class="inline-flex items-center mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-navy-700 hover:text-navy-900 transition-colors"
          >
            View consulting
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">PMO Resources</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Practical PMO resources - templates, artefacts and structured packs - for project managers, delivery leads and organisations that need stronger project control.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/pmo-resources"
            class="inline-flex items-center mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-navy-700 hover:text-navy-900 transition-colors"
          >
            Browse resources
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Digital Assets</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1">
            A growing portfolio of digital assets built around useful content, searchable information, commercial intent and repeatable systems.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/digital-assets"
            class="inline-flex items-center mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-navy-700 hover:text-navy-900 transition-colors"
          >
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Work With Lavelle Pty Ltd</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          For consulting, PMO resources, delivery support or digital asset enquiries, use the contact form to send an enquiry.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-navy-800 hover:bg-navy-900 rounded-md transition-colors"
        >
          Contact Lavelle Pty Ltd
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
